OL,3,CSainsbury's to cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,4,Cclose in-store cafes
OL,6,FJob losses at Sainsbury's head office
OL,7,Fwill happen over the next few months
OL,8,Fas the retailer says it is facing a
OL,9,F"challenging cost environment".
OL,10,FBusiness and Economics Editor Joel
OL,11,FHills reports
OL,13,FSainsbury's will cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,14,Fclose all of its in-store cafes, the
OL,15,Fsupermarket announced on Thursday.
