OL,3,CSainsbury's to cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,4,Cclose in-store cafes
OL,6,FThe redundancies would include a 20%
OL,7,Freduction in senior management roles
OL,8,Fas the supermarket giant plans to
OL,9,Ffocus on fewer, bigger roles to
OL,10,Fsimplify its head office and
OL,11,Fmanagement teams.
OL,13,FSainsbury's also said it will close
OL,14,Fits 61 remaining cafes as most
OL,15,Fshoppers do not use them, it said.
OL,17,FJob losses at the head office will
OL,18,Fhappen over the next few months.
