OL,3,CSainsbury's to cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,4,Cclose in-store cafes
OL,6,FThe layoffs represent around 2% of the
OL,7,Fcompany's current workforce of 148,000
OL,8,Femployees.
OL,10,FThe retailer's patisserie, hot food
OL,11,Fand pizza counters in-store are also
OL,12,Fset to close, with the most popular
OL,13,Fitems to be available in the aisles
OL,14,Finstead.
OL,16,FThe cuts come after Sainsbury's
OL,17,Fannounced its "biggest ever" Christmas
OL,18,Ftrading period and said profit for the
OL,19,Ffull year would likely be between
OL,20,F#1.01 billion and #1.06 billion
OL,21,Fearlier in January.
