OL,3,CSainsbury's to cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,4,Cclose in-store cafes
OL,6,F"We have had to make tough choices
OL,7,Fabout where we can afford to invest
OL,8,Fand where we need to do things
OL,9,Fdifferently to make our business more
OL,10,Fefficient and effective," he said.
OL,12,F"The decisions we are announcing today
OL,13,Fare essential to ensure we continue to
OL,14,Fdrive forward our momentum but have
OL,15,Falso meant some difficult choices
OL,16,Fimpacting our dedicated colleagues in
OL,17,Fa number of parts of our business.
OL,19,FHe said Sainsbury's would do
OL,20,F"everything we can" to support anyone
OL,21,Fimpacted by the announcements.
